\" data-lemma=\"κεῖμαι\">ΚΙΤΕ</span><span data-text=\"μόνανδρος\" data-n=\"100\" data-lemma=\"μόνανδρος\">ΜΟΝΑΝΔΡΟΣ</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic003700_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003700_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic003700.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003700-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>Text: Ferrua 1989</span>  </span>; </li><li><span class=\"line 1\">line.1: <span>IG: [--- Π]α[λλ]αδίου; CIG: [Μνημεῖον Γενν]αδίου</span>  </span><br></li><li><span class=\"line 5\">line.5: <span>IG and CIG: [Σε]π[τ]εμβρίω[ν] </span>  </span><br></li><li><span class=\"line 6\">line.6: <span>CIG: --- ἐμὸν ἃνδρ[α]</span>  </span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2> translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">  </p><p>The purchase of the tomb. Palladios, the spouse of Pelagia. Pelagia having passed 11 [days] before the Kalends of [...], having died [...] of September, here she, who had one husband, lies</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>  </p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> Gualtherus 1624 [1625] no.41 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001931\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001931</a>  </li><li> Kirchhoff 1877 9497 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001249\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001249</a>  </li><li> Kaibel 1890 <a href=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\" target=\"_blank\">530b</a>  <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072</a>  </li><li> Ferrua 1989 no.433 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001995\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001995</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence.  </div>",
