      "html": "<h2> translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">  </p><p>The purchase of the tomb. Palladios, the spouse of Pelagia. Pelagia having passed 11 [days] before the Kalends of [...], having died [...] of September, here she, who had one husband, lies</p>  "
